"""request hours data"""
data = coins.get_ohlc_cc(self.coin, self.limit, frequency='hour')
assert isinstance(data, pandas.DataFrame)
unique_values, unique_expected = helpers.find_uniques(list(data.columns.
    values), self.expected_headers)
assert unique_expected == []
if unique_values:
    pytest.xfail('Unexpected values from get_ohlc_cc(frequency=hour): {}'.
        format(unique_values))
